---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="About — 2112 Capital Solutions"
  description="Sovereignty consulting. Bitcoin integration for individuals, organizations, and operating businesses. Comprehensive education. Hands-on infrastructure support."
>
  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Streamline <em>sovereignty.</em></h1>
      <div class="hero-sub">
        Bitcoin integration · Freedom tech · Sovereignty education
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- MISSION -->
  <section class="module">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="module-classify">
        <span>MISSION</span>
        <span class="ref">WHAT WE DO &amp; WHY</span>
      </div>
      <h2 class="module-title">Helping you interface with <em>the Bitcoin economy.</em></h2>
      <p class="module-lede">2112 Capital Solutions provides hands-on Bitcoin integration and freedom tech consulting for individuals, organizations, and operating businesses. We deliver comprehensive sovereignty education and promote best practices so others can thrive in the great digital transformation.</p>
      <p class="module-lede">Our goal: streamline sovereignty. Help you build and protect your wealth outside of the traditional financial system.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- APPROACH -->
  <section class="module">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="module-classify">
        <span>APPROACH</span>
        <span class="ref">EMPOWERMENT, NOT OPPOSITION</span>
      </div>
      <h2 class="module-title">Preparation. <em>Not paranoia.</em></h2>
      <p class="module-lede">The great digital transformation is here — AI, surveillance capitalism, programmable money, agentic systems, the quiet erosion of personal data ownership. Privacy is going to suffer for everyone. Wealth held in legacy systems will face new pressures. The infrastructure most people rely on quietly belongs to someone else.</p>
      <p class="module-lede">We don't assume dystopia, and we're not selling anarchism. The answer is preparation — the same way prudent people kept fire insurance long before their house burned down. Self-custodial Bitcoin, self-hosted infrastructure, private AI, and a privacy stack are quickly becoming standard equipment.</p>
      <p class="module-lede">Three things we help you do:</p>
      <ul class="bullet-list">
        <li>Thrive in the great digital transformation</li>
        <li>Safeguard your wealth, your tools, and your time</li>
        <li>Don't get left behind</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHO WE WORK WITH -->
  <section class="module">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="module-classify">
        <span>WHO WE WORK WITH</span>
        <span class="ref">CLIENT PROFILES</span>
      </div>
      <h2 class="module-title">Hands-on engagements <em>with documented deliverables.</em></h2>
      <ul class="bullet-list">
        <li>Individuals migrating from exchange custody to self-held cold storage</li>
        <li>Operating businesses adding Bitcoin to treasury</li>
        <li>Engineering teams integrating Lightning or BTCPay</li>
        <li>Founders thinking about privacy and self-hosted infrastructure</li>
        <li>Clients who want documented deliverables, not vibes</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PRIOR ART / REFERENCES -->
  <section class="module">
    <div class="container container--narrow" style="padding: 0 var(--page-margin);">
      <div class="module-classify">
        <span>PRIOR ART</span>
        <span class="ref">PUBLIC WORK · COMMUNITY · ENGAGEMENTS</span>
      </div>

      <div class="references">
        <h6>— References &amp; prior work</h6>
        <ol>
          <li>Founder: Giovanni Ceva. Independent writing at <a href="https://thebitcoinbreakdown.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">The Bitcoin Breakdown</a> · 2022–present.</li>
          <li>WBIGAF — long-form treatise on Bitcoin's ethical &amp; economic foundations <a href="https://thebitcoinbreakdown.com/guide" target="_blank" rel="noopener">[link]</a></li>
          <li>JC Bitcoin Meetup — monthly community education in Jersey City NJ <a href="https://thebitcoinbreakdown.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">[link]</a></li>
          <li>Audited engagements: 50+ self-custody migrations · 12+ node deployments · 3 corporate treasury implementations</li>
        </ol>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
